article_title: Powerful national group spending big to sway Tennessee lawmakers

article_metadata.description: NASHVILLE -- Republican Rep. Kevin Brooks of Cleveland says all he did in January was ask fellow GOP lawmakers to keep an open mind on Republican Gov. Bill Haslam's Insure Tennessee proposal.
